oot.</P><P>Or solo...a pet with more HPS, more stackable dots than any one class has, coupled with fear AND snare.</P><P>THINK a moment, we don't have it bad, sure we stink in a lot of ways, but WHEN DO YOU STOP with the petitions.</P><P>If they gave the pets more HPs, what's next?<BR>PETTION! "We need an upgrade to ST!"<BR>PETITION! "Shaman have better DoTs than us, and they can solo better than us!"<BR>PETITION! "Fear can't land on 55+ mobs!"<BR>PETITION! PETITION! PETITION!</P><P>We should work on the pets, but not so soon after previous petition and SoL.  Besides, try out our new slows on undead...hell my pet tanks just fine once those are on.</P><P> <BLOCKQUOTE id=quote><font size=1 face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" id=quote>quote:<hr height=1 noshade id=quote>The comment you replied to, entales your regular common velious mob. Use Ebolt and Plague on the old continent, even kunark, then goto velious. Ebolt and Plague just dont land. They'll get ya summoned, but they wont fucking land. <hr height=1 noshade id=quote></BLOCKQUOTE id=quote></font id=quote><font face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size=2 id=quote></P><P>I've landed them, did you OOS/double tash/Malo the mobs? It doesn't get you summoned and killed when you let the tanks build some agro. </P><P>Typically I land more than just Vexing, but hey, you wouldn't know n uber mob if it came up and bit you on the butt (no Potus looking at the loot charts on other guild sites don't count as fighting uber mobs, I'm sorry).</P><P>And I'm quick to flame you because I'm sick of you, it's nothing but negativity.  You are ignorant of the class and think all you should have to do is /pet guard here and go off and read a porno and get tons of EXP. I'll give you this, what you lack in eloquence you make up for in pure vile hatred.</P><P>It's not my fault you're a moron Potus, but hey flame back some more, once again I won by getting you stirred up.  God you're fun.</P><P>Can you use some more obscene words please potus? It